            ">Gold Nears Record High Amid Election Buzz</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.altdaily.co/email/images/an-oct-17-1.jpg" alt="Gold Nears Record High Amid Election Buzz" href="https://www.altdaily.co"/>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Gold is <a href="https://www.investmentnews.com/alternatives/gold-approaches-another-record-as-election-race-fed-rate-cuts-come-into-focus/257722" target="_blank">surging</a> as the U.S. election approaches, with investors seeking safety amid political uncertainty. The race between Trump and Harris is tight, pushing gold close to its all-time high of $2,685. With central banks buying heavily and the potential for Fed rate cuts, gold’s appeal is growing. Market forecasts suggest the metal could reach $2,917 by next year. Even as the dollar strengthens, gold’s performance remains impressive, up 30% in 2024.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
